53
00:10:53,202 --> 00:10:54,669
Sean!

54
00:10:56,672 --> 00:10:58,503
Sean!

55
00:10:58,574 --> 00:10:59,905
One minute!

56
00:11:05,948 --> 00:11:07,540
I'm coming!

57
