72
00:12:14,183 --> 00:12:15,741
May's a great month.

73
00:12:15,818 --> 00:12:17,581
Nice and warm.

74
00:12:17,653 --> 00:12:20,087
- Well done, Joseph.
- Thank you.

75
00:12:46,148 --> 00:12:47,206
Hi.

76
00:12:47,283 --> 00:12:49,114
Are you coming
to Eleanor's party?

77
00:12:49,185 --> 00:12:51,176
No. I want to see Anna.

78
00:12:54,156 --> 00:12:56,522
