80
00:12:58,494 --> 00:13:00,325
We're gonna do the cake.

81
00:13:01,263 --> 00:13:02,594
Sorry we're late.

82
00:13:02,665 --> 00:13:04,064
In the dining room.

83
00:13:04,967 --> 00:13:06,298
Thank you.

